# Demo set for conformer generation: flexible molecules with several
# rotatable bonds, so multiple distinct 3D shapes are expected.
CC(C)Cc1ccc(cc1)C(C)C(=O)O ibuprofen
OCCCCCCO hexane-1,6-diol
CCCCCCCC octane
CC(=O)OCCN(C)C acetylcholine-ish
c1ccccc1CCCCc1ccccc1 1,4-diphenylbutane
CC(N)C(=O)NC(C)C(=O)O ala-ala-dipeptide
